          <p>(A) Oxidative phosphorylation (hsa00190), (B) DNA replication (hsa03030). In both pathways, a higher number of genes with lower variability are present in ESCs versus iPSCs. The red stars indicate a significant difference between the two groups for a specific level of expression variability.</p>
